<title>UK: RESEARCH ALERT - Amersham cut at BZW.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Amersham cut at BZW.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Amersham International Plc was cut to &quot;hold&quot; at BZW, market sources said on Wednesday.</p>
<p>The move came as Amersham shares rose sharply for a second day following the company's merger with Norway's Nycomed.</p>
<p>Further detail on BZW's downgrade was not immediately available and analysts at the brokerage could not be reached for comment.</p>
<p>Amersham shares were up 85p at 17.67-1/2 stg by 0930 GMT, after on Tuesday gaining 87-1/2p.</p>
<p>-- David Holmes, London Newsroom +44 171 542 4367</p>
